name: en-osm_viewer_v2_assam
title: World Maps & Satellite Photos
description:
Search for cities/towns with more than 1000 people. There are about 127,654 worldwide:

  • Worldwide maps with satellite photos: 10 levels of zoom with 305-metre resolution
  • South Asia maps: 15 levels of zoom + 4 levels of overzoom (building details & natural geography)
  • Satellite photos of Northeast India, Bangladesh, Bhutan: 19-metre resolution
extra_description: Thank you to the OpenStreetMap community, making it possible for anybody to improve these maps for the benefit of all.
